title: Fables 068-069/077-080/100 (Dgtl-HR|Nahga-Empire) (FULL RE-RIPS)
description:
Overview:  <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fables_%28comics%29" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fables_%28comics%29</a>


Contains:   A handful of "Fables" re-rips, released a few weeks ago and meant as
            replacements for those issues in the big Fables set by Nahga-Empire
            (from April 2013, see e.g.  <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9012946" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9012946</a>
            and  <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9869890" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9869890</a>   ), all of which were
            incomplete in one way or another. The specifics are listed below.


    - Fables 068-069 (2008)      (Digital) (F) (Nahga-Empire)

      restore previously missing text (see samples from original rip and re-rip):

        <a href=" http://image.bayimg.com/ff58b7f7ec87da66979d02cf6888830f524babd1.jpg" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://image.bayimg.com/ff58b7f7ec87da66979d02cf6888830f524babd1.jpg</a>
        <a href=" http://image.bayimg.com/5b8225f252a59a4349cf0bb045fcd158011ce8cb.jpg" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://image.bayimg.com/5b8225f252a59a4349cf0bb045fcd158011ce8cb.jpg</a>


    - Fables 077-080 (2008-2009) (Digital) (F) (Nahga-Empire)

      restore the previously missing "Jungle Book" backup serials (see cover image).


    - Fables 100     (2011)      (Digital) (F) (Nahga-Empire)

      restores one of the previously missing illustrated tales (pages ~70 thru ~80).
